TradeHill,provides,an,online,tool,that,allows,users,to,freely,buy,and,sell,the,decentralized,internet,commodity,known,as,Bitcoin,The,Trading,API,allows,developers,to,interact,their,applications,directly,with,TradeHill,The,functions,available,are,broken,up,into,two,groups,Public,Data,Functions,which,do,not,require,users,to,authenticate,and,Trading,Functions,which,require,authentication,data,to,be,specified,along,with,the,request,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON,and,JSONP